subject: Volleyball
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: The top-ranked Penn State women’s team won its 92nd straight match to tie the mark for the second-longest winning streak in N.C.A.A. Division I team sports. The two-time defending national champion Nittany Lions swept visiting Northwestern, 25-20, 25-14, 25-20.
